Executive Profile
Sophie A. Gasperment  Chief Executive Officer, The Body Shop International plcAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships53--
Background

		Ms. Sophie A. Gasperment served as the Chief Executive Officer of The Body Shop International plc from July 2008 to October 2013. Ms. Gasperment has been Group General Manager of L'Oréal Financial Communication and Strategic Prospective since 2014. She held multiple marketing and general management positions at L’Oréal since joining in September 1986, including Managing Director of L’Oréal UK and Ireland, from January 2004 to January 2008. After 14 years in operational ... and strategic marketing positions developing brands and product/service innovations, she was appointed General Manager of L'Oréal Paris, then of the L'Oréal group, in the UK. She remained UK based for the next 14 years, notably as Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of The Body Shop International, the emblematic English brand spanning 60 countries and ca. 20,000 people strong. She serves as a Member of Supervisory Board of Cimpress N.V. She has been an Independent Director of Accor S.A. since June 29, 2010. She was appointed French Foreign Trade Advisor in 2005 and elected to the UK Executive board. She is also a member of the Business Advisory Council of Saïd Business School, Oxford University. Ms. Gasperment is a graduate of ESSEC business school and of Insead.Read Full Background




