Sophie Gasperment

Age : 53Linked companies :  L'Oreal SA -  Accor SA -  Cimpress NV 





Summary 



Ms. Sophie Gasperment is Member-Supervisory Board at Cimpress NV and Group General Manager-Financial Communications at L'Oréal SA.She is on the Board of Directors at Cimpress NV and Accor SA. Ms. Gasperment was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by BSI USA, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Buth-Na-Bodhaige, Inc., Managing Director & Director by L'Oreal (UK) Ltd., Chairman by Skin & Hair Care Preparations, Inc., and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by The Body Shop International Plc.She also served on the board at Anderbarn Ltd., Body Shop Germany Gmbh, Browndray Ltd., Cranvine Ltd., Creektime Ltd., Crestsold Ltd., Dishmax Ltd., Enfranchise Ninety One Ltd., Fillcare Ltd., Groundmesh Ltd., Islemend Ltd., L'Oreal Golden Ltd., Leasetime Ltd., Lordmark Ltd., Masonride Ltd., Modesite Ltd., Soapworks Ltd., Solitaire Fashion Shops Ltd., The Body Shop (Isle of Man), The Body Shop Beteiligungs-GmbH, The Body Shop Card Services Ltd., The Body Shop Midlands Ltd., The Body Shop Queenslie Ltd., The Body Shop Retail Properties Ltd., The Body Shop South-West Ltd., The Millennium Administration Ltd. and Toteview Ltd.She received her undergraduate degree from INSEAD and an undergraduate degree from ESSEC Business School.



